This paper discusses machine translation approaches that rely on Semantic Web technologies, which involve natural language processing and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
